<section class="get_in_touch_area" id="contact"><div class="container"><div class="l_title" style="padding-bottom: 25px"><h6 style="">SmrtBook</h6><h2 style="">FAQs for help</h2></div><div class="row get_touch_inner"><div class="col-lg-6"><div id="accordionF" role="tablist" class="solution_collaps"><div class="card"><div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingOneF"><h5 class="mb-0"> <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOneF" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOneF"> What do SmrtBook.in offer? <i class="minus">-</i> <i class="plus">+</i> </a></h5></div><div id="collapseOneF" class="collapse show" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOneF" data-parent="#accordionF"><div class="card-body"><p>SmrtBook offers an Online Examination platform that help you conduct exams online. With SmrtBook, your exam will be hosted in minutes</p></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingTwoF"><h5 class="mb-0"> <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseTwoF" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwoF"> What are the key benifits of using SmrtBook? <i class="minus">-</i> <i class="plus">+</i> </a></h5></div><div id="collapseTwoF" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwoF" data-parent="#accordionF"><div class="card-body"><p>With SmrtBook, you can host an exam in minutes, you will have control in your hands. Update exams anytime, get complete exam analytics, student analytics and each question analytics. We also provide student dashboard for students and their parents where they can access their previous exams, results and analytics.</p></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingThreeF"><h5 class="mb-0"> <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseThreeF" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThreeF"> How is SmrtBook.in Different from others? <i class="minus">-</i> <i class="plus">+</i> </a></h5></div><div id="collapseThreeF" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThreeF" data-parent="#accordionF"><div class="card-body"><p>SmrtBook's Examination interface works without internet once started, the student need not have an internet connection during the exam. Only for starting and submiting the exam, you will be required to have an internet connection. This way, a slow internet connection won't affect your exam performance.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="col-lg-6"><div id="accordionFF" role="tablist" class="solution_collaps"><div class="card"><div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingOneFF"><h5 class="mb-0"> <a data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseOneFF" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOneFF"> What is an Online Examination Interface? <i class="minus">-</i> <i class="plus">+</i> </a></h5></div><div id="collapseOneFF" class="collapse show" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOneFF" data-parent="#accordionFF"><div class="card-body"><p>An Online examination interface lets you host your offline exams online. With every other thing getting digital, a shift towards online entrance examination is must. Although online interface will increase efficiency for the system, it will bring new challenges for students to adjust.</p></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingTwoFF"><h5 class="mb-0"> <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseTwoFF" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwoFF"> What are other advantages of using an Online Interface? <i class="minus">-</i> <i class="plus">+</i> </a></h5></div><div id="collapseTwoFF" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwoFF" data-parent="#accordionFF"><div class="card-body"><p> We help you provide a Personalised Interface that help you practice better. Also, with the mobile friendly interface you can access your progress reports anywhere.</p></div></div></div><div class="card"><div class="card-header" role="tab" id="headingThreeFF"><h5 class="mb-0"> <a class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapseThreeFF" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThreeFF"> What kind of analytics can SmrtBook.in provides? <i class="minus">-</i> <i class="plus">+</i> </a></h5></div><div id="collapseThreeFF" class="collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingThreeFF" data-parent="#accordionFF"><div class="card-body"><p> SmrtBook provides each student's personalised progress report. Their response time, comparison with topper students and with batch average too. Overall coaching performance with performance of all students in every question can be used to design improvment plans for a specific batch.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div> </section>

